Cuke4AS3 Developer is a alpha/protoype to allow actionscript to be used for cucumber step definitions

Wiki Home:
https://github.com/flashquartermaster/Cuke4AS3/wiki

How to use Cuke4AS3 Developer:
https://github.com/flashquartermaster/Cuke4AS3/wiki/How-To-Use-Cuke4AS3

Source comming soon

New in Version 0.3.2

Cuke4AS3Lib
Table support for tables where the headers are the first column in the table

Cuke4AS3 Developer UI
Fixed: Server Errors not being reported

Cuke4AS3
Cuke4AS3.stop() now ensures that the steps being run are destroyed if stop is called in the middle of an executing scenario